So would you put your trust in him? And if you've taken him out of those scenarios in your mind,

00:13:38.464 --> 00:13:44.224
My encouragement to you today is be aware of that and put him back in those scenarios and let him go.

00:13:44.416 --> 00:13:46.336
Calm the storms in your life.

00:13:46.240 --> 00:13:47.200
Amen.

00:13:46.912 --> 00:13:48.192
Let's pray together.

00:13:48.032 --> 00:13:49.408
Jesus, we love you.

00:13:49.536 --> 00:13:51.776
We're so thankful to be a part

00:13:52.064 --> 00:13:53.312
of your kingdom.

00:13:53.376 --> 00:13:59.712
To be sons and daughters of the Most High God. And we say thank you for that, Lord, knowing that there are storms, that there's chaos,

00:13:59.872 --> 00:14:03.104
Because there are spiritual battles that are happening all around us.

00:14:03.008 --> 00:14:06.848
But Lord, we don't have to fear because you are in the boat with us. Amen.

00:14:06.976 --> 00:14:08.512
that you have power over

00:14:08.256 --> 00:14:10.336
Over those spiritual forces

00:14:10.176 --> 00:14:11.744
And God, that you are.

00:14:11.744 --> 00:14:14.720
Showing up in ways that we may not yet understand.

00:14:14.944 --> 00:14:18.592
You're not walking in fear, Lord. You are the sovereign God.

00:14:18.784 --> 00:14:23.296
of the entire universe, lord over everything that we see and everything that we don't see you.

00:14:23.136 --> 00:14:24.608
Our King of Kings.

00:14:24.448 --> 00:14:28.928
And so we confess that, Lord, if there is an area of our life that we have walked in fear, that

00:14:29.152 --> 00:14:35.744
Lord, would you reveal that to us and let us put you back in those scenarios, in our minds, the scenarios that haven't even happened yet?

00:14:35.712 --> 00:14:37.696
And the scenario is that may never happen.

00:14:37.504 --> 00:14:41.920
Lord, we have removed you from those areas and from those scenarios, and we repent of that. Amen.

00:14:41.696 --> 00:14:43.424
so god would you teach us?

00:14:43.488 --> 00:14:48.608
Would you teach us to be about your mission, even if you tell us no to our dreams or desires?

00:14:48.352 --> 00:14:53.664
or maybe it's a relationship, maybe it's a job, maybe it's a move that you've told us no.

00:14:53.696 --> 00:14:59.200
"'Maybe no forever, or maybe no for right now. "'But, God, you've told us no, "'I pray that we would trust you in that.'"

00:14:59.488 --> 00:15:06.016
And Lord, because you're teaching us to follow you and you're teaching us that you have something greater at work. You have a plan at work.

00:15:06.208 --> 00:15:08.768
And you are inviting us into your plan.

00:15:08.832 --> 00:15:12.064
And so God, help us trust you, increase our faith.

00:15:11.904 --> 00:15:16.096
Lord, remove our fear, and would you please perfect us in your love.

00:15:15.968 --> 00:15:19.200
We love you, Jesus, and we ask all of this in your name.

00:15:19.392 --> 00:15:20.640
Amen.
